{"text": "This modern, designer-furnished 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina features views of the Little Fatra and Martinky. The layout of the apartment is ideal for those who want to enjoy the benefits of a high position without the need for air conditioning, as it does not overheat during summer months. The living room has access to a balcony that runs the entire width of the living room, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The bedroom is furnished with a double bed and nightstands, while the children's room serves as an office for women. The bathroom features a bidet shower by the toilet, underfloor electric heating, and a washing machine and dryer. The apartment has been meticulously designed to meet both functional and practical purposes, including high-quality materials used in every room, including the furniture. The entrance door is security and fire-resistant, with non-standard aluminum floor strips in a titanium shade. The kitchen features built-in appliances (induction hob, BOSCH dishwasher) and a sliding kitchen table with designer base."}
